      "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You're wielding a gun.</p><hr /><p>You target a creature's limbs or other appendages to weaken them. You Aim, then make a ranged Strike at your mark. If the Strike hits, the creature becomes your choice of @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.i3OJZU2nk64Df3xm]{Clumsy 1} or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled 1} until the end of your next turn (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.i3OJZU2nk64Df3xm]{Clumsy 2} or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled 2} on a critical hit).</p>"
